high_descs: Turn right, walk forward towards the table, turn right and face the oven.
Pick up the pan that is on the bottom left burner.
Turn left, walk forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Open the top doors of the fridge and put the pan on the top shelf. Close the fridge doors, wait a few seconds, open the fridge door, take the pan out, close the fridge door.
Turn left, walk forward, turn left, walk forward, turn left and take a step back until you see the kitchen counter on the right..
Open the the cabinet door on the bottom right, place the pan inside, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan in the bottom cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right when you reach the stove.
Pick up the pan from the front left burner of the stove.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf of the fridge, then take it out.
Face the cabinet to the bottom left of the fridge.
Place the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled pan in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn and cross the room to face the left side of the stove.
Pick the pan up from the stove.
Go left and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door, pick up the pan and shut the door.
Go to the right and face the lower cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Put the pan in the lower cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan in the cabinet.
